          .why.left
            h2 Why use uRequire ?
            p Cause module formats are incompatible in almost all terms: syntax, execution environment, capabilities, dependency/path resolution, plugins etc. But you need to write <em>in one</em> of them, not all. And then you need to execute in all. uRequire does exactly this.

